    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_11_28753-28838",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "28753-28838",
      "markText": "黄药师当然怒极，但因自己其时立誓不离桃花岛一步，心愿未偿，不能自违毒誓、出岛追捕，暴跳如雷之际，竟然迁怒旁人，将余下弟子一一挑断大腿筋脉，尽数逐出了桃花岛，自己闭门生气。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=28753&rangeEnd=28838",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=28753&rangeEnd=28838"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_51_6754-6846",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "6754-6846",
      "markText": "郭靖想到杨康和穆念慈之事，不胜感叹，心想：“杨康是我义弟，结义兄弟该当是有福共享，有难同当。他如今误入歧途，我不能不理，说什么也要劝得他改邪归正才是。”斜倚在舱内船板之上，呆呆的出神。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=6754&rangeEnd=6846",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=6754&rangeEnd=6846"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_8_2028-2060",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2028-2060",
      "markText": "钱塘江浩浩江水，日日夜夜无穷无休的从临安牛家村边绕过，东流入海。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2028&rangeEnd=2060",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2028&rangeEnd=2060"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_27_8262-8295",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "8262-8295",
      "markText": "完颜洪烈觉得他手掌发热，心中大喜，道：“我做李渊，你做李世民罢。”",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=8262&rangeEnd=8295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=8262&rangeEnd=8295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_40_16028-16043",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "16028-16043",
      "markText": "欧阳克跌下棺盖，已自气绝而毙。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=16028&rangeEnd=16043",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=16028&rangeEnd=16043"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_55_17533-17591",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "17533-17591",
      "markText": "郭靖心情激动，说道：“是的，找十年，找二十年，我总是要去找她。找十年，找二十年，我总时时刻刻记得你在这草原上等我。”",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=17533&rangeEnd=17591",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=17533&rangeEnd=17591"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_15_21282-21324",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "21282-21324",
      "markText": "黄蓉低声道：“你再体惜我，我可要受不了啦。要是你遇上了危难，难道我独个儿能活着么？”",
      "totalCount": 196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=21282&rangeEnd=21324",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=21282&rangeEnd=21324"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_36_3047-3115",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "3047-3115",
      "markText": "突然间身上一松，船帆从头顶揭起，只见洪七公提着船头的铁锚，以锚爪钩住了横桁，正在将帆拉开。却是洪七公不忍见他就此活活烧死，当即出手相救。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=3047&rangeEnd=3115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=3047&rangeEnd=3115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_22_32477-32549",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "32477-32549",
      "markText": "两人按辔缓行，一路游山玩水，乐也融融，或旷野间并肩而卧，或村店中同室而居，虽然情深爱笃，但两小无猜，不涉猥亵。黄蓉固不以为异，郭靖亦觉本该如此。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=32477&rangeEnd=32549",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=32477&rangeEnd=32549"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_22_17514-17578",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "17514-17578",
      "markText": "刚转了这个念头，只见王处一拄着一根木杖，颤巍巍的走过来。师兄弟三人一照面，都是一惊，万料不到全真派中武功最强的三人竟会都受了伤。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=17514&rangeEnd=17578",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=17514&rangeEnd=17578"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_22_24045-24104",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "24045-24104",
      "markText": "穆念慈心中另有一番打算，她自己早把终身付托给了完颜康，心想他既是爹爹的亲生骨血，当然姓杨，自己如也姓杨，婚姻如何能谐？",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=24045&rangeEnd=24104",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=24045&rangeEnd=24104"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_22_29375-29409",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "29375-29409",
      "markText": "“用不着说。我不能没有她，蓉儿也不能没有我。我们两个心里都知道的。”",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=29375&rangeEnd=29409",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=29375&rangeEnd=29409"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_16_20556-20629",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "20556-20629",
      "markText": "穆念慈在一旁听两人叙旧，便想出言提醒，要郭靖先救他们出去，再慢慢谈论，忽然转念一想：“这一出去，只怕永远见不到他啦。”一句话刚到口边，又缩了回去。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=20556&rangeEnd=20629",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=20556&rangeEnd=20629"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_22_16901-16994",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "16901-16994",
      "markText": "完颜康心想：“难道我要舍却荣华富贵，跟这穷汉子浪迹江湖？不，万万不能！”他主意已定，高声叫道：“师父，莫听这人鬼话，请你快将我妈救过来！”丘处机怒道：“你仍是执迷不悟，真是畜生也不如。”",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=16901&rangeEnd=16994",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=16901&rangeEnd=16994"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_36_29918-29993",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "29918-29993",
      "markText": "欧阳克低声道：“别这么大声，给叔叔听到了，他可放你不过。我早知道啦，死在你的手里，我一点也不怨。”黄蓉叹了口气，心道：“这人虽然讨厌，对我可真不坏。”",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078116&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=29918&rangeEnd=29993",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6f632d50813ab8503g0163a2?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=29918&rangeEnd=29993"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078116_28_14390-14452",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "14390-14452",
      "markText": "有一日他忽然想到：“倘若双足也能互搏，我和他二人岂不是能玩八个人打架？”但知此言一出口，势必后患无穷，终于硬生生的忍住不说。",
